# VHS tape: superseo-skills page-audit demo
# Render with: vhs demo/demo.tape

Output demo/page-audit-demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1400
Set Height 820
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 0ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Padding 24
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 36
Set Margin 18
Set MarginFill "#11111b"
Set BorderRadius 10

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "bash demo/demo-runner.sh"
Sleep 200ms
Enter

Sleep 24s
